{
  "texts": [
    "Furthermore, the technological boom after COVID-19 brought us ChatGPT, whose impact is far more significant than technology ever had in the past.",
    "It could impact all processes of knowledge management in organizations.",
    "It was also validated in the response when ChatGPT was asked about its impact on knowledge management in organizations (see Table I).",
    "Chat GPT could be used in organizations to enhance their knowledge management processes and thus inform decision-making by reshaping knowledge",
    "creation, transfer, sharing, and application."
  ]
}